{"tid":191039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環職員兼休班輔警拳毆同事被捕","createTime":"2017-04-07T14:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T14:19:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1df74192a19783e5c2e885a3262dfd486259c96d","tid":191039,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"旺角洗衣街148號食環署環境衛生總辦事處，前晚11時許，一名姓郭(36歲)男職員及一名姓倪(50歲)男職員因工作問題爭執，期間倪疑揮拳襲擊郭，有人見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查後，以涉嫌普通襲擊拘捕倪，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。倪為一名休班輔警警員，他已獲准保釋候查，須於下月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n食環署證實事件，署方一向重視員工紀律，若發現員工有違規行為，該署會按既定程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"afc941503158bd20a70b0ec7b0a852c87353f54d","tid":191039,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"食兩家茶飯咁爽"},{"pid":"364b9051b4b00549651214bf36631e0479ab0d99","tid":191039,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c05a4ed2e5a762c6bd16365913c6b765f40a2c","tid":191039,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"最後果兩段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c972c23e571125695284581bb2d7a527127460","tid":191039,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"傻仔，你落毒毒佢又得，等佢去廁所先打又得"},{"pid":"b7262f882bb1b090d56633d89838e3e387950242","tid":191039,"uid":25506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"連自己友都打埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04baa02b432842f27288e9cbb72f1093b9c91fa1","tid":191039,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:16:5